Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme song playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] The human whose name\Nis written in this notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,shall die…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Takuo laughs] Woo!\N-[Lady] Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Now… what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,TAKUO SHIBUIMARU\NACCIDENTAL DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Any human who's used a Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,can neither go to heaven nor hell\Nfor eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I want the world to know\Nof my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's someone passing\Nrighteous judgement on the wicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become the God of this New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,CONFRONTATION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[teacher] He found himself overwhelmed\Nwith happiness and satisfaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[girl] I have no idea what he was thinking\Ncoming to my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am so through with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[boy] Seriously? So, what happened\Nwith your dad after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[teacher] Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yagami?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please recite this line for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Having finally made his dream a reality,\Nhe was overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Both by the magnitude of his achievement,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and by the joy and happiness\Nthat it brought him."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That was very well done,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not surprised, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely flawless. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,\Nwe'll leave it at that for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-[chairs scraping]\N-[footsteps receding]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[bell ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-[students chatter]\N-[Ryuk] I thought it'd never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do this every day?\NIt's so boring here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light! Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[quietly] Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike you, people can still hear me\Nwhen I talk out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, well aren't you boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-We were just going to head down to the--\N-Sorry, I'm a little busy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have anything to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you just going to go home\Nand hang out in your room, as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NOf course, I have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[news reporter] There was more violence\Nacross the city today. Another stabbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This time at a restaurant in the heart\Nof the Kabuki-cho district of Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[chomping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. Hey, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[swallows] I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Why are you working so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I can't afford to waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a very small window\Nto write names in this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have from when I get\Nhome from school until I go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I still need to sleep,\Nso I can maintain my average
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I can't be sleeping in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, there's all the studying at home\Nand at cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let myself get too tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It will start to affect my health\Nand my mental performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm serious\Nabout trying to create an ideal world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that's free from evil
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then I need to make the most of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu] Huh? Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light, what's going on?\NWhy is your door locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It's Sayu.\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu] Can you help me with my homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing quadratic equations in math.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt.\NI know you're studying right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm like the only person in my class\Nwho doesn't get this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be careful if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone else touches that notebook\Nyou've got hidden in the drawer right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll be able to see me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He waits till now to mention\Nthat important detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Hm? It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what exactly don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you stuck on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu] Um… well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[delegate 1] There have been 52 deaths\Nthat we're aware of,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's just in the past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[delegate 2] Every single one of them\Ninvolved a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[delegate 1] They were all criminals\Nwho were either being held in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or who were wanted by police\Nfor outstanding crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think it's safe to say\Nthere are other criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,whose deaths are unaccounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case the death toll\Ncould be well over 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… morning, Chief.\NThey started the meeting without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. I had to take an urgent call\Nfrom headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, these were criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who were probably\Nfacing execution sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we shouldn't be--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should it matter\Nif it's a criminal or someone innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I checked,\Nmurder was still murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still too early\Nto consider these a homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how did all these people have\Nheart attacks at the exact same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not coincidence, it's murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's possible
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to simultaneously kill all these people\Nin different locations?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're treating this as\Nan elaborate murder plot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that's been carried out by\Na large organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is a large organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'm not alone\Nin suspecting the FBI or CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[delegate] I dare you to say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, this is not the time\Nto be joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to confirm that these\Nare indeed homicides and not coincidences!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How? Autopsy results show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that in all of these cases, the victims\Ndied of a sudden heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigating a series of heart attacks\Nis pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what else we can learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If these people had been shot or stabbed,\Nat least we'd have something to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, it looks as if\Nwe'll have no choice but to bring in L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[delegates muttering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Chief. What's this "L"\Nthey're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I forgot that it's your first time\Nat this conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know L's real name\Nor whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we still don't even know\Nwhat he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he's managed to solve every case\Nhe's ever taken on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's tackled some of the greatest\Nmysteries this world has ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He hides in the shadows,\Nbut he's the best of the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A last resort. Our trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[delegate] But I've heard this "L"\Nis extremely arrogant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand he'll only take on cases\Nthat he's personally interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we don't even know\Nhow to contact him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] L is already on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Gentlemen, L has already begun\Nhis investigation into these incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[delegate] Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That man's the only known person\Nwho can contact L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows his true identity either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-[murmuring]\N-[Watari] Please be silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,L would now like to address the delegates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[L, voice altered via voice distorter]\NGreetings to all of you at the ICPO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] What are we doing here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand why we're\Nsneaking around this dump. Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? You told me that anyone\Nwho touches the Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,will be able to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to carry something\Nthis dangerous with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that if my family\Never saw the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell them I was keeping records\Nof various criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in preparation\Nfor becoming a detective one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm walking a very fine line\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I make one mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I might end up killing my own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] The difficulty of this case lies\Non its unprecedented scope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And make no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We are witnessing an atrocious act\Nof mass murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,one that is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This case cannot be solved\Nwithout the full cooperation of the ICPO.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all of the police organizations\Nyou represent throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to make the decision to fully\Nsupport the investigation at this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I require additional cooperation\Nfrom Japan's National Police Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why Japan in particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Whether the guilty party\Nis an individual or a group,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a strong possibility\Nthat they are Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if they are not,\Nwe can be sure they're hiding in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this based on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Why Japan, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I will be able to provide you\Nwith proof of that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,after I directly confront the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A direct confrontation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] At any rate, I would like to set up\Nthe investigation headquarters in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was easier to make\Nthan I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean\Nyou were able to hide the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I hid it right here in this drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't seem to be\Nparticularly well hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You left the key in the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] And that's the whole point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I intentionally left the key
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in the most noticeable place\NI could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just a regular diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that once most people\Nfind the diary inside my desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll probably satisfy their curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But... the real key...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just an everyday item you'd expect\Nto find lying around on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A regular ball-point pen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and all I need is this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] So that's the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If you look closely,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find that there's a small hole\Nunderneath the drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you just insert this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Aha. A fake bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The diary will distract most people,\Nso I doubt anyone will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] But that's not all.\N-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if someone figures out\Nthat there's a fake base,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've set things up\Nso that there's no way they could
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,get their hands on the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,once the ink reservoir is inserted,\Nit acts as an insulator,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,preventing the flow of electricity\Naround this circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When the fake base of the drawer's\Nput back,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,this piece of rubber\Nalso prevents the flow of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if someone were to try
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and force the bottom of the drawer open,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the circuit would connect
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and now would ignite the gasoline\Ncontained in this thin plastic casing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,instantly setting the notebook on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I’ve got it set up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,all the evidence\Nwould be completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm ever questioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just say\Nthat I was hiding the real diary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because I didn't want anyone to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a pretty believable excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... it is my diary after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of humans finding Death Notes\Nin the past
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and typically,\Nthe biggest problem they had
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is finding a good place to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, Light, you're probably the first\Nto have given it this much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, it's a pretty risky setup\Nfrom the look of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make even the slightest mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you could be badly burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Risky?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You say\Nthe strangest thing sometimes, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole thing has been a risk\Nsince the very beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,from the moment I obtained the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but compared to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,this doesn't even qualify as a risk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it actually protects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It all comes down to a choice:\Nwould I prefer to be executed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,or deal with a little house fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[announcer] Last night\Nin the West Tokyo penitentiary,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki Koro Kitayama, originally sentenced\Nto 15 years for armed robbery,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was reported to have died\Nof a sudden heart attack at the age of 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the most recent death\Nin a steadily growing number
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of cases involving inmates\Ndying of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] This is unbelievable.\NCriminals are dropping like flies lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 2] It's a little scary,\Nbut at the same time, it's kinda cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] Just make sure\Nyou don't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 3] I wouldn't be surprised\Nif the police were behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 2] No way.\NThe police don't have that kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't you know about him?\N-[student 3] Hmm? About who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] Kira. You know, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 4] I wonder\Nwho's gonna be killed next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA, KILL EVERYONE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,SEND MESSAGE?\NSEND
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[computer chimes]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,NAME: ROCOCO\NKIRA, KILL EVERYONE - NAME: MISERY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] Ryuk, you should check this out.\N-[Ryuk] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Websites like this\Nare popping up everywhere lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] "The Legend of Kira the Savior."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Sounds pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I think\Nthey've taken the name "Kira"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,from the English word "killer."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't say I'm too happy about that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it looks like that's the name\Nthey've decided to give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When I search the word Kira, I'm pulling\Nup tons of sites just like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The media hasn't picked up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still calling this\N"a succession of unexplained deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,among the world's\Nmost hardened criminals."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the people of the world can already sense\Nthat there's something happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They know there's someone out there\Npassing righteous judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Human beings are like that, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Although this would probably\Nnever happen in school,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say that students\Nwere asked to discuss
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,whether bad people deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can bet that everyone would\Ngive the politically correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just wrong to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's what they're bound to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's the correct response\Nto give, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans will always try\Nto maintain appearances
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,when they're in public.\NThat's just how we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is how they really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Most are too afraid to support me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as they’re worried about\Nwhat others will think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Many would rather deny my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the Internet,\Nwhere you can remain anonymous,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,support for Kira is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe people are afraid\Nto say it out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but they all understand what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's making the bad guys\Ndisappear one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have done no wrong\Nare cheering for Kira in their hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because they have nothing to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,while those who have done wrong\Nare on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're forced to hide\Nfrom an unknown enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going just like I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,THE PROGRAM IS INTERRUPTED\NFOR A SPECIAL BROADCAST
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to apologize\Nfor the interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now we're bringing you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a live worldwide broadcast\Nfrom Interpol's ICPO.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Interpol?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[announcer]\NWe now take you live to the ICPO.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I head up\Nan International Police Task Force
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,which includes all member nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Lind L. Tailor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise known as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro] So this is how it all begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] But, sir, I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never actually\Nshown his face before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he choose to do it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-It must mean L's serious about this.\N-Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,L, we've followed every single one\Nof your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time for you to prove\Nwhat you said to the ICPO.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Criminals around the world\Nare being murdered by a serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider this crime to be the most\Natrocious act of murder in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not rest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,until the person or persons responsible\Nare brought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira, I will hunt you down.\NI will find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems certain he'll catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. That fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll never find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll have to get this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And as long as the police don't find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,there won't be any evidence\Nto convict me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,which means that catching me\Nwill be absolutely impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I anticipated that the police\Nwould get involved
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and that something like this might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira, I've got a pretty good idea\Nwhat your motivation might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can guess what you hope to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However,\Nwhat you're doing right now is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You think… I'm evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I protect the innocent\Nand those who fear evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who will become the god\Nof a new world that everyone desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All those who would oppose that god,\Nthey are the ones who are truly evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're just too stupid, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This could've been a lot more interesting\Nif you'd only been a bit smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[pen scratching]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show the world what happens\Nwhen you cross me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire world is watching… L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Five more seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs maniacally]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NYou got nothing else to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] [through distorter]\N[gasps] I had to test this, just in case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I-- I never thought\Nit would actually happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems you can kill people\Nwithout having to be there in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have believed it\Nif I hadn't just witnessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you did, indeed, kill Lind L. Tailor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the man who you just saw\Ndie on television,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I should tell you that he was an inmate\Nwhose execution was scheduled for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] The police arrested him\Nin absolute secrecy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so you wouldn't have heard about him\Non TV or through the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that not even you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,have access to information\Nabout these types of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He got you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] But I assure you, L is real.\NI do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,try to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] You… you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] What's wrong? Hurry up.\N-[man 1] What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] Come on, right now. Kill me!\N-[man 1] He's really taking this too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[man 2] Are you trying\Nto kill yourself, L?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-[bystander 1] What's going on?\N-[bystander 2] Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-it's Kira versus L!\N-[L] Come on. What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[bystander 3]\NA live broadcast of a killing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] You better do it.\NCome on, Kira, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-[bystander 4] Amazing!\N-[bystander 5] Do it, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-[bystander 6] Someone, stop this!\N-[L] What's the matter? Can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light exhales shakily]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Well Kira, it seems that you\Ncan't kill me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[in normal voice]\NSo, there are some people you can't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've given me a useful hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[distorted] Let me return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you something\Nthat I think you'll find interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Although this was announced\Nas a worldwide broadcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we are only broadcasting\Nin the Kanto region of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I had planned to broadcast this message\Naround the world until we found you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but it looks like that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I now know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This L guy is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] The police treated your first killing\Nas an unrelated incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but in actuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the first of your victims\Nwas a suspect in Sinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the criminals that have recently\Ndied of heart attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,this one's crime was, by far,\Nthe least serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, his crime was\Nonly ever reported inside Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[in normal voice] I used that information\Nto deduce this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[distorted] You are in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and your first victim was little more\Nthan an experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which means you haven't been killing\Nfor very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] We decided to broadcast in Kanto first
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because of its large population,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and, luckily, we found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To be completely honest with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected that things\Nwould go this well…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but it won't be too long now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,before I'll be able to sentence you\Nto death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,L has…\Ncertainly lived up to his reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhmm. He proved that Kira exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that the deaths were murders,\Nand that he is here in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I am very interested to know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,how you're able to commit these murders\Nwithout being present…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't mind waiting\Na little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[in normal voice]\NYou can answer all of my questions
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,when I catch you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[distorted] Let's meet again soon, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light exhales]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna sentence me to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept your challenge, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of them has to hunt down the other\Nwithout knowing the other's name or face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And the first one\Nwhose identity is revealed will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,L...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[L and Kira] I will hunt you down\Nwherever you're hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will eliminate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-I am...\N-I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[L and Kira] ... justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme song playing]